<li><a href="http://pricetheory.uchicago.edu/levitt/Papers/LevittJuvenileCrimePunishment1998.pdf" class="external text" title="http://pricetheory.uchicago.edu/levitt/Papers/LevittJuvenileCrimePunishment1998.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Juvenile Crime and Punishment."</a> 1998, <i>Journal of Political Economy</i>, <i>106</i>(December): 1156-1185.</li>
