stein_Library" title="Regenstein Library">Regenstein Library</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/The_Renaissance_Society" title="The Renaissance Society">Renaissance Society</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Robie_House" title="Robie House">Robie House</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rockefeller_Chapel" title="Rockefeller Chapel">Rockefeller Chapel</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Seminary_Co-op" title="Seminary Co-op">Seminary Co-op</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Shoreland_Hotel" title="Shoreland Hotel">Shoreland Hotel</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Smart_Museum_of_Art" title="Smart Museum of Art">Smart Museum of Art</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Snell-Hitchcock" title="Snell-Hitchcock">Snell-Hitchcock</a></span></div>
