iki/Richard_Posner" title="Richard Posner">Richard Posner</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/James_Heckman" title="James Heckman">James Heckman</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/David_D._Friedman" title="David D. Friedman">David D. Friedman</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Kevin_M._Murphy" title="Kevin M. Murphy">Kevin M. Murphy</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><strong class="selflink">Steven Levitt</strong>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/John_A._List" title="John A. List">John A. List</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span></p>
